message.body: Unless something crazy comes up at work this afternoon, I'll be ready for a swim at 6.
Yay! Same here. I'll text if anything changes, if not I'll see you at the pool.

I hope not :-( As bad as it is right now, the radar is really spotty. There's a chance it might clear up in time
Running late as usual but on my way.
